data.description: Gorgeous home shows like a model! This home delivers all that you need with beautiful interior finishes,  a well thought out spacious floorplan, a kitchen for all culinary skill levels including the Chef who loves to prepare culinary delights. Highly desired open great room floorplan perfect for entertaining  with split bedrooms. Marbella is a central location near many activities such as the State Farm AZ Cardinals Football Stadium, Westgate shopping, dining, and Luke AFB and employment.  The Marbella community has parks and greenbelt areas. Create your own backyard paradise.
